<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1848:1875'>地官鄉師及葬執纛以與匠師御匶<span class='krp-note'>古柩/字</span>而治役註云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1875:1898'>匠師事官之屬其於司空若鄉師之於司徒也鄉師主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1898:1921'>役匠師主衆匠共主葬引纛翳也即羽葆也執以指麾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1921:1934'>輓柩之役正其行列進退也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1934:1960'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '019-8a' );" name="019-8a" class="pb">[019-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
