<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2010:2034'>夏官方相氏掌蒙熊皮黄金四目𤣥衣朱裳執戈揚盾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2034:2057'>大喪先匶謂葬使之前導以郤凶惡也及墓入壙以戈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2057:2066'>擊四隅敺罔兩也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2066:2092'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '019-9a' );" name="019-9a" class="pb">[019-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
